item.title: Exploring Telangana's District Data: A SQL Analysis
item.description: In this project , we delve into the world of data and databases to analyze various aspects of Telangana’s districts. Our dataset comprises information from multiple tables related to revenue, vehicle sales, and industrial sectors in Telangana. We will conduct SQL queries to extract meaningful insights and provide suitable analysis for each result.
